  "title": "Retail Sales Associate",
  "description": "<p><strong>Working day:</strong> 6 days (Rest day fall on weekday)</p><p><strong>Working hour</strong>: Retail Working Hour (11am-10pm, can leave at 9pm if no booking)</p><p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p><p>• 5-20% performance related pay (PRP) per month</p><p>• 2% medical pay per month</p><p>• Annual salary increase</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Test, familiarize yourself with, and stay updated on all VR games offered in the store.</li><li>Guide customers through game rules and usage procedures to ensure a safe and enjoyable experience.</li><li>Oversee the operation of VR gaming stations and perform basic technical troubleshooting (e.g., PC, VR system, VR game setup).</li><li>Conduct VR equipment maintenance and minor repairs (training will be provided).</li><li>Assist customers with enquiries, recommend suitable game packages, handle bookings, and close sales.</li><li>Perform daily operational duties such as cashiering, cleaning, and sanitizing equipment.</li><li>Ensure good customer service standards are maintained.</li><li>Carry out any other reasonable duties as assigned by the Company aligned with the scope of the role.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Passion and interest in VR/gaming entertainment.</li><li>Basic PC operation and troubleshooting skills.</li><li>Customer service oriented, with good communication and interpersonal skills.</li><li>Friendly, diligent, proactive, and able to work in a fast-paced environment.</li><li>Able to work independently and as part of a team.</li><li>Experience in retail, entertainment or service industry will be an added advantage.</li><li>No prior experience is required. Training will be provided. Candidates who are keen to learn and willing to be trained are encouraged to apply.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Maxhunt Resource Pte Ltd | EA Licence: 22C1322<br />Cynthia Lai | Registration No: R25146301</p>",
